      "rationale": "Qualitative equivalency table prepared mapping validation experiment parameters to COU parameters. Blood analog viscosity within 6% of clinical blood viscosity at operating shear rates. Geometric equivalency confirmed via CAD comparison. Formal equivalency metric not required at MRL 2."
